          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Thoracic Society</ENAMEX> guidelines [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">30</TIMEX> ] . To derive forced
          expiratory volume in <TIMEX TYPE="TIME">one second</TIMEX> (FEV 
