          <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">277</NUMEX>) and <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">women</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">n</ENAMEX> = <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">418</NUMEX>) separately. We chose the model
